5.6  Recommendations:
Require the completion of the physical inventory report and determine the insurable properties;
Instruct the General Services Officer to officially request the GSIS to conduct evaluation of properties for the consideration in the insurance plan coverage;
Direct the General Services Officer to coordinate with the Municipal Budget Officer in the estimation of premiums that may be incurred for the insurance plan; and
Advise the Municipal Budget Officer to appropriate the necessary amount to cover for the payment of premiums for the insurance of the properties in annual budget.
5.7 We further recommend strict compliance with R.A. No. 656 (Property Insurance Law) to ensure that all identified insurable assets belonging to the Municipality of Tubaran are adequately covered /insured with GIF of the GSIS.
